description:
<!--StartFragment-->

The song amazing grace,is a song that celebrates the grace we have received through the death, burial and resurrection of our Lord Jesus Christ. It's amazing that as little as man is, God loved us enough to send his son to die for us so that we will be qualified for His great amazing grace.

This indeed is worth singing about.

I know that as you listen the spirit of God will minister to you, as you sing praises to God for his amazing grace.

<!--EndFragment-->
